      {
        "text": "###Farming \n\n**Farmers use AI to study their fields.** Computers look at pictures from satellites or drones to check:\n\n- If plants are healthy 🌿\n\n- If the soil needs water 💧\n\n- If plants are sick and how to help them.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/5070c391e8172d47ff37a6c9abdbf6dc-Career Exploration Panels.png",
        "key": "hardware-components-e56bb056-0af5-475f-b8e1-7b49f9c79f82",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "typing": false,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "####Health Data Expert\n- They use AI to find patterns in health data.\n- This helps doctors spot problems early.\n- Their work makes care smarter and faster! 🩺💻\n\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/9a1b911244e99755d70970256b620b5d-Career Exploration Panels.jpg",
        "key": "hardware-components-ed2b07b1-278f-49d5-ba3b-02994f4bccd8",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "###Fitness App Coder\n\n- They use code and AI to track moves and workouts.\n- Apps give smart tips to stay healthy.\n- Tech that helps you stay active! 🏃‍♀️📱\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/c46b4437fb3f3bc340eaf11608dc2261-Career Exploration Panels (1).png",
        "key": "test-elem-career-journeys-explore-panels-efeae7e1-8db4-4614-b904-07eedf4ef555",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      }
    ],
